text: Král ulice is a 1935 Czechoslovak romantic drama film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Karel Hašler, Markéta Krausová, and Helena Bušová. ==Cast== *Karel Hašler as Martin Antoni *Markéta Krausová as Martin's wife *Helena Bušová as Martin's daughter Helena *Jára Kohout as Jura *Oldrich Vykypel as Jan Pokorný, violinist *Sylva Langova as Nanynka, Pokorný's sister *Milada Smolíková as Márinka Heinrichová, housewife by Martin *Bedřich Vrbský as the Police inspector *Zdenek Gina Hasler as Robert Stanley ==References== ==External links== *Král ulice at the Internet Movie Database Category:1935 films Category:Czechoslovak romance films Category:1935 romantic drama films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak drama films Category:Czechoslovak black-and-white films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:1935 drama films
